WWII History - December 2014  USA

88 Pages | True PDF | English | 12 MB 

WWII History Magazine is the foremost authority on the greatest war in history. Each issue covers the famous battles, little-known incidents and usually forgotten sidebars to put you right in the action. Every issue has dozens and dozens of rare photographs, colorfully crisp paintings and meticulously detailed drawings culled from the biggest and best archives in the world
